---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import FeatureSection from '../components/FeatureSection.astro';
---

<Layout title="ScriptHookVDotNet">
  <div class="section-base-container">
    <div class="shvdn">
      <div class="shvdn-container">
        <Header />
        <div class="hero">
          <section>
            <h1>Concise. Powerful. Productive.</h1>
            <p class="hero-desc">
              <strong>ScriptHookVDotNet (SHVDN)</strong> is a script runtime that
              runs under Script Hook V. SHVDN hosts .NET Framework scripts and acts
              as an interface between custom .NET code and Grand Theft Auto V for
              Story Mode. SHVDN offers you an easier scripting environment for GTA
              V with guided APIs than what Script Hook V offers for C++ scripts.
            </p>
          </section>
          <section class="download-section">
            <section class="download-button-groups">
              <section class="download-button-group-nightly">
                <a
                  class="download-button download-button-nightly"
                  role="button"
                  href="https://github.com/scripthookvdotnet/scripthookvdotnet-nightly/releases/latest"
                >
                  Latest Nightly
                </a>
                <a
                  class="download-button-prev-vers download-button-nightly-prev-vers"
                  role="button"
                  href="https://github.com/scripthookvdotnet/scripthookvdotnet-nightly/releases"
                >
                  Previous Nightly Versions
                </a>
              </section>
              <section class="download-button-group-stable">
                <a
                  class="download-button"
                  role="button"
                  href="https://github.com/scripthookvdotnet/scripthookvdotnet/releases/latest"
                >
                  Latest Stable
                </a>
                <a
                  class="download-button-prev-vers"
                  role="button"
                  href="https://github.com/scripthookvdotnet/scripthookvdotnet/releases"
                >
                  Previous Stable Versions
                </a>
              </section>
            </section>
            <p class="download-note">Note: PC version only</p>
          </section>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <section class="section-body-container">
      <section class="feat-section-container">
        <FeatureSection
          title="Write scripts with comfort and powerful .NET ecosystem"
        >
          <p>
            SHVDN lets you create .NET scripts without having to learn C++.
            Create your scripts with the help of APIs written in the
            object-oritented style. You can use arbitrary .NET Framework
            libraries, too.
          </p>
        </FeatureSection>
        <FeatureSection
          title="More guided scripting API interfaces, faster test cycle"
        >
          <p>
            Scripting APIs provide interfaces organized more than native
            functions GTA V provides for their script "threads", which can be
            instantiated by ysc script container files or ASI scripts. SHVDN
            provides document for well-known APIs and usages, and it reduces
            time spent testing the behaviors of native functions for typical
            usages.
            <br />
            Although the SHVDN runtime cannot be reloaded after Script Hook V unloads
            all the loaded ASI scripts once for now, SHVDN offers the ability to
            reload the entire SHVDN runtime, and SHVDN scripts can be reloaded by
            executing the reload command of SHVDN.
          </p>
        </FeatureSection>
        <FeatureSection title="Non-aggressive limitation removal">
          <p>
            SHVDN removes some limitations that custom scripts cannot encounter
            by accident (thus non-aggressive), such as despawning GTA Online
            vehicles, prop (object) model check, and player model check.
            <br />
            To let your game customizable as possible, SHVDN will not remove any
            limitations that custom scripts can encounter without decent care, such
            as linear and angular velocity limits.
          </p>
        </FeatureSection>
      </section>
      <section class="requirements">
        <h2>Requirements</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>
            <a href="http://www.dev-c.com/gtav/scripthookv/">Script Hook V</a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a
              href="https://dotnet.microsoft.com/download/dotnet-framework/net48"
            >
              Microsoft .NET Framework 4.8+
            </a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a
              href="https://support.microsoft.com/en-us/help/2977003/the-latest-supported-visual-c-downloads"
              >Microsoft Visual C++ Redistributable Package for Visual Studio
              2019+ (x64)
            </a>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          Note: Microsoft .NET Framework 4.8 is pre-installed in Windows 10 and
          Windows 11, and Rockstar Games Launcher installs Microsoft Visual C++
          Redistributable Package for Visual Studio 2019.
          <br />
          So you should only need to have Script Hook V installed in the usual case.
        </p>
      </section>
    </section>
  </div>

  <script></script>

  <style>
    :root {
      --colors-primary-cyan: #00afea;
      background-color: #1d1d22;
      --background-color-rgb: 29, 29, 34;
      --text-color-rgb: 255, 255, 255;
      color: white;
      --hero-bg-filter: brightness(55%) blur(2px);
    }

    @media (prefers-color-scheme: light) {
      :root {
        --colors-primary-cyan: #1466b8;
        background-color: #f4f2ff;
        --background-color-rgb: 244, 242, 255;
        color: #121212;
        --text-color-rgb: 18, 18, 18;
        --hero-bg-filter: blur(2px);
      }
    }

    body {
      font-family: Open Sans, sans-serif;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-rows: 1fr auto;
      grid-template-columns: 100%;
      min-height: 100vh;
    }

    h1,
    h2,
    h3,
    h4,
    footer {
      font-family: Inter, sans-serif;
    }

    .feat-section-container {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 24px 0;
    }

    .shvdn-title {
      font-family: Open Sans, sans-serif;
    }

    .hero {
      padding: 24px 16px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;

      display: grid;
      grid-template-rows: 100%;
      grid-template-columns: [section-start] 6.5fr [section-end] 0.5fr [download-start] 2.5fr [download-end];
    }

    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 48px;
    }

    .hero-desc {
      font-size: 20px;
    }

    .download-container {
      flex-basis: 33%;
    }

    .download-section {
      text-align: center;
      grid-column-start: download-start;
      grid-column-end: download-end;
    }

    @media (max-width: 720px) {
      .hero {
        flex-direction: row;
        grid-template-rows: auto;
        grid-template-columns: auto;
      }

      .download-section {
        text-align: center;
        grid-column-start: auto;
        grid-column-end: auto;
      }
    }

    .download-button-groups {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: [nightly-group-start] 1fr [nightly-group-end] 16px [stable-group-start] 1fr [stable-group-end];
    }

    .download-button-group-nightly {
      grid-column-start: nightly-group-start;
      grid-column-end: nightly-group-end;
    }

    .download-button-group-stable {
      grid-column-start: stable-group-start;
      grid-column-end: stable-group-end;
    }

    .download-button {
      display: block;
      padding-left: 40px;
      padding-right: 40px;
      padding-top: 24px;
      padding-bottom: 24px;
      border-width: 2px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      min-width: 260px;
      font-weight: 600;
      background-color: #1379d8;
      color: #1a1a1b;
      font-size: 24px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-family: Inter, sans-serif;
    }

    @media (max-width: 1280px) {
      .download-button {
        min-width: 200px;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 1024px) {
      .download-button {
        min-width: 0;
      }
    }

    .download-button:hover {
      background-color: rgb(46 139 226);
    }

    .download-button-prev-vers {
      display: block;
      padding-top: 8px;
      padding-bottom: 8px;
      font-weight: 600;
      background: none;
      color: #64aaeb;
      font-size: 18px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-family: Inter, sans-serif;
    }

    .download-button-prev-vers:hover {
      color: #9bc3e9;
    }

    .download-button-nightly {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #ecc045;
      background-color: rgb(26, 26, 27);
    }

    .download-button-nightly:hover {
      color: rgb(241, 205, 103);
      background-color: rgb(26 26 27 / 0.7);
    }

    .download-button-nightly-prev-vers {
      color: #f5e58d;
    }

    .download-button-nightly-prev-vers:hover {
      color: #faf4d3;
    }


    @media (prefers-color-scheme: light) {
      .download-button {
        background-color: #233dcc;
        color: #e8e8e8;
      }
      .download-button:hover {
        background-color: #1e54c9;
        color: #e8e8e8;
      }

      .download-button-prev-vers {
        color: #07132c;
      }

      .download-button-prev-vers:hover {
        color: #3056b1;
      }

      .download-button-nightly {
        color: #f8d122;
        background-color: rgb(26, 26, 27);
      }
      .download-button-nightly:hover {
        color: rgb(252, 215, 50);
        background-color: rgb(26 26 27 / 0.9);
      }

      .download-button-nightly-prev-vers {
        color: #332c0e;
      }

      .download-button-nightly-prev-vers:hover {
        color: #7c6c2a;
      }
    }

    .download-note {
      margin-top: 8px;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .shvdn {
      background: url(/images/bg-dark-mode.jpg) no-repeat 50% 70% / cover;
    }

    @media (prefers-color-scheme: light) {
      .shvdn {
        background: url(/images/bg-light-mode.jpg) no-repeat 50% 50% / cover;
        background-size: cover;
      }
    }

    .shvdn-container {
      background-image: linear-gradient(
        rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 92.5%,
        rgba(var(--background-color-rgb), 0.45) 96.25%,
        rgba(var(--background-color-rgb), 0.8) 100%
      );
      background-position: center center;
      background-repeat: no-repeat;
      background-size: cover;
      min-height: 70vh;
      -webkit-backdrop-filter: var(--hero-bg-filter);
      backdrop-filter: var(--hero-bg-filter);
    }

    @media (prefers-color-scheme: light) {
      .shvdn-container {
        -webkit-backdrop-filter: var(--hero-bg-filter);
        backdrop-filter: blur(2.5px);
      }
    }

    .section-body-container > * {
      padding: 24px 16px;
    }

    .requirements ul {
      list-style: disc;
      margin: 0 0 2em 0;
      padding-left: 2rem;
    }

    .system-requirement ul li {
      padding-left: 0.5em;
    }

    .requirements p {
      opacity: 0.675;
    }
  </style>

  <style is:global>
    .reinforced-ragdoll-velocity-snippet {
      padding: 8px;
    }
  </style>
</Layout>
